data.description: New two car detached garage 27 by 24 with 9 foot walls, New AC 2 1/2 ton. 2 year old furnace, 2 year old New roof, New Vinyl Siding with high r padding, Concrete Versatile Sidewalk with Ramp,  24 Slot Electrical Box, Inflatable Hot Tub in Basement, New Gas Stove, New  Dishwasher, New Laminate flooring in Living Room, Master Bed and Kitchen, 2 other bedrooms have original oak floors. New Double Pane All Vinyl Windows in Bedrooms and Kitchen.  New Six Panel Doors throughout, Big  back yard 8100 sq ft with a six foot privacy fence, Easy Walk to Grade School. Recently expanded concrete driveway provides access to large 2 car garage. Basement and old garage being converted to bedrooms. Needs kitchen cabinets/countertop.   $240,000.00 or best offer.
data.whatILove: Highly energy efficent home have utility bills to prove it. New double pane all vinyl windows in bedrooms and kitchen. Basement recently vapor locked. House still has a huge fenced in back yard even with a new 24 by 27 garage. Reroofed in 2013. New two and a half ton ac. Furnace bought in 2014. Have 9 permits from village for a home improvements. Basement has an inflatable hot tub. Gas stove. Laminate floors in living room, master bedroom and kitchen. Main bath has a new waterfall shower.  Home will be sold soon.
